caption.text: The key to happiness is to always have control over your emotions.

Graduation day, 23rd may 2015.
Once, someone told me that highschool wasn't going to be easy. But it will be worth it.
Friends aren't one of a kind.. They're unique.
They "sometimes" can be annoying, and become the most ungrateful people you've ever met. But, if you're patient enough, you'll be able to know that best things come from pain.
It's just the thing about life.. you never know who will come to stay, or suddenly vanish in the blink of an eye.
Be grateful with what you have, don't ask for more, or less.
Thanks for these past (almost) 3 years.
